---
// Game landing page for Builder Station
---

<html>
  <head>
    <title>Builder Station | ephergent.com</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@900&family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      body {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a1a 0%, #1a1a2e 50%, #0a0a1a 100%);
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
        color: #e0e0e0;
      }
      .game-hero {
        font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
        color: #0ff1ce;
        text-shadow: 0 0 20px #0ff1ce88;
      }
      .tagline {
        color: #0ff1ce;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        text-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff1ce44;
      }
      .nav-link {
        color: #fff;
        border: 2px solid #0ff1ce;
        border-radius: 1.5rem;
        padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.2s;
        display: inline-block;
      }
      .nav-link:hover {
        background: #0ff1ce;
        color: #0a0a1a;
      }
      .game-card {
        background: rgba(10,16,32,0.8);
        border: 1px solid #0ff1ce33;
        border-radius: 1rem;
        padding: 2rem;
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .specs {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
        gap: 0.75rem;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      .spec-item {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 0.25rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #0ff1ce22;
      }
      .spec-label {
        color: #0ff1ce88;
      }
      .scanlines {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0; left: 0; width: 100vw; height: 100vh;
        pointer-events: none;
        background: repeating-linear-gradient(
          to bottom,
          transparent, transparent 6px,
          #0ff1ce08 7px, transparent 8px
        );
        z-index: 10;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden p-8">
    <div class="scanlines"></div>
    <div class="game-card">
      <h1 class="game-hero text-4xl font-black mb-2 text-center">BUILDER STATION</h1>
      <p class="tagline text-center mb-8">An ancient structure in the Space between worlds. Pixel and Clive explore what was left behind. Clive remembers more than he says.</p>

      <div class="specs">
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Genre</span><span>Exploration</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Engine</span><span>Godot 4</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Size</span><span>14.9 MB</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Season</span><span>2</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Character</span><span>Pixel Paradox</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Price</span><span>Free forever</span></div>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #a0a0b0;">
        Builder Stations float in the Space between frequencies. They are ancient — older than any of the five known frequencies. They emit a stabilizing signal that keeps the cosmic dial from drifting apart. Without them, frequencies fade. The Space becomes silence.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #a0a0b0;">
        Most went dark eight hundred years ago, during The Dimming. A few still broadcast, faintly. A1 uses them for navigation, reading the dying signals like lighthouses in fog.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #a0a0b0;">
        Pixel and Clive have docked at Station 7-Ascending. The station is active. It has been expecting them. Clive goes very still when they enter the main atrium. He says: "It remembers me." He does not say: "I don't remember it remembering me." Pixel notices. She does not ask. Not yet.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-row justify-center gap-4 mt-8">
        <a href="/games/builder-station/play/" class="nav-link font-bold">Play Now</a>
        <a href="/games/builder-station/about/" class="nav-link">About</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
